- Tested search, update and delete from Tab 3 to make sure the new service methods work correctly with the existing page logic.
- Tracked down and fixed TypeScript/template errors on Tab 3 related to the Item interface and service methods so the page would compile cleanly and talk to the API correctly.
- Refined Tab 3 behaviour and navigation by adjusting routing and reusing shared service methods where possible to keep the code simpler and more consistent.
